 aprendidas durante la jornada de la vida</a>”, <em>Liahona,</em> mayo de 2001, pág. 38; tomado de un discurso pronunciado por el élder Wirthlin en una charla fogonera del SEI en BYU el 7 de noviembre de 1999.</p></li><li class="footnote" id="note8-"><span class="label">8. </span><p data-aid="134802787" id="note8_p1"><a class="scripture-ref" href="/scriptures/ot/ps/30.5?#4" old-href="../../../../scriptures/ot/ps/30.html?verse=5#p5">Salmos 30:5</a>.</p></li><li class="footnote" id="note9-"><span class="label">9. </span><p data-aid="134802789" id="note9_p1">Véase <a class="scripture-ref" href="/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/27.13?#12" old-href="../../../../scriptures/bofm/3-ne/27.html?verse=13#p13">3 Nefi 27:13</a>.</p></li><li class="footnote" id="note10-"><span class="label">10. </span><p data-aid="134802790" id="note10_p1">Véase <a class="scripture-ref" href="/scriptures/nt/luke/12.7?#6" old-href="../../../../scriptures/nt/luke/12.html?verse=7#p7">Lucas 12:7</a>.</p></li><li class="footnote" id="note11-"><span class="label">11. </span><p data-aid="134802791" id="note11_p1">Véase <a class="scripture-ref" href="/scriptures/nt/matt/10.29?#28" old-href="../../../../scriptures/nt/matt/10.html?verse=29#p29">Mateo 10:29</a>.</p></li><li class="footnote" id="note12-"><span class="label">12. </span><p data-aid="134802792" id="note12_p1"><a class="scripture-ref" href="/scriptures/pgp/abr/2.8?#7" old-href="../../../../scriptures/pgp/abr/2.html?verse=8#p8">Abraham 2:8</a>.</p></li><li class="footnote" id="note13-"><span class="label">13. </span><p data-aid="134802793" id="note13_p1"><a class="scripture-ref" href="/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/64.29?#28" old-href="../../../../scriptures/dc-testament/dc/64.html?verse=29#p29">Doctrina y Convenios 64:29</a>.</p></li><li class="footnote" id="note14-"><span class="label">14. </span><p data-aid="134802794" id="note14_p1">Carta de Aida Chilan, 20 de abril de 2017.</p></li><li class="footnote" id="note15-"><span class="label">15. </span><p data-aid="134802795" id="note15_p1">Carta de Aida Chilan, 30 de mayo de 2017.</p></li><li class="footnote" id="note16-"><span class="label">16. </span><p data-aid="134802796" id="note16_p1"><a class="scripture-ref" href="/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/84.88?#87" old-href="../../../../scriptures/dc-testament/dc/84.html?verse=88#p88">Doctrina y Convenios 84:88</a>.</p></li><li class="footnote" id="note17-"><span class="label">17. </span><p data-aid="134802797" id="note17_p1">Véase <em><a class="cross-ref" href="/manual/teachings-joseph-smith/chapter-30" old-href="../../../../manual/teachings-joseph-smith/chapter-30.html">Enseñanzas de los Presidentes de la Iglesia: José Smith,</a></em> 2007, págs. 371–380.</p></li><li class="footnote" id="note18-"><span class="label">18. </span><p data-aid="134802798" id="note18_p1"><a class="scripture-ref" href="/scriptures/bofm/hel/4.24-25?#23" old-href="../../../../scriptures/bofm/hel/4.html?verse=24-25#p24">Helamán 4:24–25</a>.</p></li><li class="footnote" id="note19-"><span class="label">19. </span><p data-aid="134802799" id="note19_p1"><a class="scripture-ref" href="/scriptures/nt/rom/8.28?#27" old-href="../../../../scriptures/nt/rom/8.html?verse=28#p28">Romanos 8:28</a>.</p></li><li class="footnote" id="note20-"><span class="label">20. </span><p data-aid="134802800" id="note20_p1"><a class="scripture-ref" href="/scriptures/pgp/moses/1.39?#38" old-href="../../../../scriptures/pgp/moses/1.html?verse=39#p39">Moisés 1:39</a>.</p></li><li class="footnote" id="note21-"><span class="label">21. </span><p data-aid="134802801" id="note21_p1"><a class="scripture-ref" href="/scriptures/ot/prov/3.5-6?#4" old-href="../../../../scriptures/ot/prov/3.html?verse=5-6#p5">Proverbios 3:5–6</a>.</p></li></ol></footer>
